"{\"uid\": \"komonews.com-news-local-edmonds-police-arrest-2-people-after-several-shootings-along-olympic-view-drive-surveillance-search-warrant-investigation-crime-drive-by-shooting-arrested-gunshots-k9-units\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Now  47\\u00b0  Sat  51\\u00b0  Sun  52\\u00b0  byChelsea Hylton, KOMO News Staff  EDMONDS, Wash. -TheEdmonds Police Departmentarrested two people and is seeking a third after a three-week spree of shootings along Olympic View Drive.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 48, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KOMO-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KOMO News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KOMO-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KOMO-TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police arrested a 37-year-old man and a 26-year-old woman, both from Lynnwood for a drive-by shooting.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lynnwood_Transit_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1124201346150476e-18, \"text\": \"Lynnwood\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lynnwood_Transit_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lynnwood_Transit_Center\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In early June, police received numerous calls from community members about sounds of gunshots around the 8100 block of Olympic View Drive.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police said most of the calls came in the late evening and overnight hours.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During their investigation police were able to find evidence showing that multiple different weapons were being used in the area.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some trees and a stop sign were shot.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 24, a resident called police to report that a gunshot had entered their home.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During this time, authorities were surveilling the area to try and identify those responsible.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 27, multiple officers established a \\\"dedicated surveillance\\\" and saw a vehicle enter the area then shortly after they heard multiple gunshots.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police said they found the vehicle unoccupied in the residential area.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After a search with the assistance of two K9 units from Edmonds and Everett, King County's Guardian 1 helicopter, and a drone unit they were able to locate two suspects.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_dog\", \"score\": 0.9999999998851763, \"rank\": 1.1486416156155005e-10, \"text\": \"K9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_dog\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police_dog\"}, {\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_County,_Washington\", \"score\": 0.9990687706103191, \"rank\": 0.0006387106743661856, \"text\": \"King County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_County,_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King_County,_Washington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police also recovered a handgun during their arrest.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A search warrant was served on the suspect vehicle where additional items of evidence were found.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Police are still investigating this incident and are searching for anyone else involved in the shootings.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If anyone has any information on these shootings they are asked to contact Edmonds police.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2025Sinclair, Inc.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}]}"